2004-04-01 17:23  gnome444

	* modules/: projects/addedit.php, projects/do_project_aed.php,
	projects/projects.class.php, tasks/tasks.class.php: Finish merge of
	Handco's import task, task dependancy patch. This fixes the task
	importing feature and also allows the importing of task into
	non-empty projects, shifting the dates of the imported tasks
	relative to the start date of the project. Dependant tasks, (not
	dynamic), now have their dates automatically adjusted when the end
	date of the task they are dependant on changes. It also changes the
	getAllowedRecords and getDeniedrecords in the projects class to not
	allow access to projects that are under companies that are denied.

