2004-01-14 22:12  robertoibarra

	* modules/tasks/do_updatetask.php: Fixed issue with international
	characters in cost codes, cost codes will now be saved in standard
	ISO since accented letters, eg., take up more than one character
	position in the database and not all of what you saw on the field
	was actually saved in the database, now everything will be except
	that characters will not be accented.

