2003-11-28 07:24  kripper

	* ChangeLog: Changelog update

2003-11-28 02:51  dylan_cuthbert

	* modules/system/: domodsql.php, viewmods.php: added "upgrade"
	option for modules, the upgrade function in the module's setup.php
	file will be called with the old version no. if the version no. in
	the setup.php is newer If you are unable to upgrade return false -
	if the upgrade succeeded return true and the module's new config
	will be automatically saved
	
	Also added confirmation yes/no dialogs for the deletion or
	upgrading of a module

