2003-09-28 16:16  kripper

	* modules/tasks/do_task_aed.php: Joined "task deleted" message
	string. Reason: atomic-wise translation doesn't work for some
	languagues.  For example (in spanish), "task" = "tarea", "deleted"
	= "eliminado", "task deleted" = "tarea eliminad_a_".

