	single, unified code base.

2002-07-08 11:48  ottenhoffs

	* logincheck.php: fixed the setcookie call by removing the third
	param ("session").  the third param should be the expiration time
	(an int).  http://www.php.net/manual/en/function.setcookie.php

2002-07-05 06:47  ajdonnison

	* includes/header.php, includes/leftnav.php,
	modules/companies/addedit.php, modules/companies/index.php,
	modules/files/index.php, modules/forums/index.php,
	modules/forums/viewer.php: Changes to remove absolute paths so that
	dotproject can be installed at any location.

2002-07-05 06:45  ajdonnison

	* includes/config.php: New config items to support date format
	control, admin email address, and to centralise site-specific
	details.

2002-07-05 06:44  ajdonnison

	* calendar.php, includes/main_functions.php: Added configurable
	date formatting.  Based upon config.php item.

2002-07-05 06:42  ajdonnison

	* modules/calendar/day_view.php: No longer reports an error when no
	events on day view.

2002-07-05 06:41  ajdonnison

	* modules/calendar/addedit.php: Broken javascript fixed to work on
	both IE and Netscape.

2002-07-05 06:40  ajdonnison

	* modules/tasks/: addedit.php, index.php, view.php: Date formats
	now controlled by config.php value.  Durations now correctly
	calculated.  Comments now shown correctly if they have embedded
	newlines.

2002-07-05 06:37  ajdonnison

	* modules/projects/: addedit.php, index.php, view.php: Date
	formatting now controlled by config.php item.  Task counts now
	correct on front page.

2002-07-05 06:30  ajdonnison

	* includes/gateway.pl: Notification email now differentiates
	between new tickets and followups.  Originator now gets a more
	detailed email that includes a subject that supports immediate
	followups.

2002-07-04 13:53  jbflowers

	* docs/CHANGELOG.txt: Minor changes and update CHANGELOG.txt

